query: M&S simply food, convenience store, York, England
name: M&S Simply Food
review_text: Always a bit of a gamble what you'll pay here. A lot of the shelf tickets don't correspond to the items on the shelves, being instead for similar products or a different size of the product you're buying. Then even if you find the right shelf ticket, when you get to the till it'll be a different price again. Sometimes you win, sometimes you lose, it probably balances out.  Only way to know for sure is stick to reductions, which are very good value.
